        Check out my newest YouTube video!

This is my experience entering an improvement season after being in prep. So much happens after stepping off stage that so many people don't see. Everyone shows the highlights. The glamour. The sparkle. But what many don't show is the aftermath. What happens after prep? Goals change. Weight gain. Distorted body image. These are a few things that some competitors face during their improvement season. I can only speak from my experience. Everyone is different. Everyone handles prep different. Same goes for an off season. I hope my experience can give some insight to any competitors out there or anyone thinking about competing. â€¢
