uldn't quite pull it off.  That attempted smile made my day.  I just stared at her for the rest of the time, trying to memorize her face and the moment.  Itâ€™s very strange, this death thing.  My whole being rebels against the fact that everyone on this earth will eventually die at some point.  Doesnâ€™t seem right.  Here I am, going 'round in circles, always to end up at exactly the same spot where I left off.  If anyone says ANYTHING about â€˜the circle of lifeâ€™, Iâ€™ll cream them with a rolled up Disney poster.  ;)  Love you, guys, and thanks fer listening.     Christi 
